        "subject": "LU-12628 lnet: do not assert on resend of msg_rx_committed",
        "message": "LU-12628 lnet: do not assert on resend of msg_rx_committed\n\nWe should only resend messages that have msg_tx_committed, but we\nneedn't assert on this condition in lnet_health_check. If\nmsg_tx_committed is not set we can simply return -1 to finalize the\nmessage.\n\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <hornc@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I184e74235bdde5cca3f1ae3e853f12c5de535159\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
